{"title": "Permission issues with dovecot stats-writer", "date": "July 11, 2019", "author": "Sim", "tags": [["email", "/tags/email"], ["postfix", "/tags/postfix"], ["dovecot", "/tags/dovecot"], ["Debian", "/tags/debian"], ["spamassassin", "/tags/spamassassin"]], "summary": "Today I encountered an error when trying to receive new messages from my mailbox.", "slug": "/terminal/2019/07/11/permission-issues-with-dovecot-stats-writer/", "html": "<p><strong>Env:</strong> Debian 10</p>\n<p>Today I encountered an error when trying to receive new messages from my mailbox.<br />\nThen I checked <code>/var/log/mail.log</code> and found this:  </p>\n<table class=\"codehilitetable\"><tr><td class=\"linenos\"><div class=\"linenodiv\"><pre><span class=\"normal\">1</span></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"na\">Jul 11 10:54:00 mail postfix/pipe[27149]: 0A3FBDBE26: to</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&lt;xxx@snorl.ax&gt;, orig_to=&lt;sim@snorl.ax&gt;, relay=spamassassin, delay=1.4, delays=0.45/0.02/0/0.98, dsn=2.0.0, status=sent (delivered via spamassassin service (lda(xxx@snorl.ax,)Error: net_connect_unix(/var/run/dovecot/stats-writer) failed: Permission denied))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>I googled and found this solution<sup id=\"fnref:1\"><a class=\"footnote-ref\" href=\"#fn:1\">1</a></sup> work well. Just append the following settings to <code>/etc/dovecot/dovecot.conf</code>:  </p>\n<table class=\"codehilitetable\"><tr><td class=\"linenos\"><div class=\"linenodiv\"><pre><span class=\"normal\"> 1</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 2</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 3</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 4</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 5</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 6</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 7</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 8</span>\n<span class=\"normal\"> 9</span>\n<span class=\"normal\">10</span>\n<span class=\"normal\">11</span>\n<span class=\"normal\">12</span>\n<span class=\"normal\">13</span></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"na\">service stats {</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">unix_listener stats-reader {</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">user</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">vmail</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">group</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">vmail</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">mode</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">0660</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"na\">unix_listener stats-writer {</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">user</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">vmail</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">group</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">vmail</span>\n        <span class=\"na\">mode</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s\">0660</span>\n    <span class=\"na\">}</span>\n<span class=\"na\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p>Then restart dovecot:  </p>\n<table class=\"codehilitetable\"><tr><td class=\"linenos\"><div class=\"linenodiv\"><pre><span class=\"normal\">1</span></pre></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">sim</span><span class=\"nv\">@mail</span><span class=\"err\">:</span><span class=\"o\">~</span><span class=\"err\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sudo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">systemctl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">restart</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">dovecot</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</td></tr></table>\n<div class=\"footnote\">\n<hr />\n<ol>\n<li id=\"fn:1\">\n<p><a href=\"https://forum.iredmail.org/post67035.html#p67035\">net_connect_unix(/var/run/dovecot/stats-writer) failed (Page 1) \u2014 iRedMail Support \u2014 iRedMail</a>&#160;<a class=\"footnote-backref\" href=\"#fnref:1\" title=\"Jump back to footnote 1 in the text\">&#8617;</a></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>", "category": "Terminal"}